sequenceDiagram
    participant H as Human Expert
    participant P as Preference Model
    participant DE as Differential Evolution
    participant BO as Bayesian Optimization
    participant S as Simulation
    
    Note over DE,BO: Candidate Generation
    DE->>S: Evolve() → Candidate A
    BO->>S: Propose() → Candidate B
    
    Note over S: Evaluation
    S->>S: Simulate both candidates
    S-->>DE: Performance metrics
    S-->>BO: Performance metrics
    
    Note over BO: Knowledge Sharing
    BO->>BO: Update with both A and B
    
    Note over H,S: Human Feedback
    S->>H: Display trajectories + metrics
    H->>H: Compare and decide
    
    alt Prefer A (DE)
        H->>P: Select Prefer DE
        P->>P: Update weights toward A
        P->>DE: Inject anchor
        P->>BO: Preference nudge
    else Prefer B (BO)
        H->>P: Select Prefer BO
        P->>P: Update weights toward B
        P->>DE: Inject BO + anchor (2×)
        P->>BO: Self-reinforcement
    else TIE (Refine)
        H->>DE: Refine bounds
        H->>BO: Refine bounds
    else REJECT (Expand)
        H->>DE: Expand bounds
        H->>BO: Expand bounds
    end
    
    Note over DE,BO: Next Iteration
